<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2022-02-04 13:21:12.734058</lastBuildDate><item><title>check out these gorgeous designs</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/pCPnRRx</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PDmfPCR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>On gorgeous women.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/k0dPxUN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Created by Buki Ade, a Nigerian American fashion designer.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ORF5PuD.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bhHOXIH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/k0rRIx6.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Born and raised in Nigeria, Buki’s family emigrated from Nigeria to the US when she was 8 years old. As the first born of a traditional Nigerian family, Ms. Ade was expected to study medicine and take care of her family with a “guaranteed” income.

In fact, she dutifully obliged by enrolling in nursing school. Ultimately, she decided to explore her own creative path.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rFeloLT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JYY4d4v.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>While on vacation one day, Ms. Ade was frustrated by the lack of diversity in the design of the swimsuits. None of the options spoke to the Afrocentric exceptionalism she desired to present. 

This, she attributed to the lack of diversity – more specifically the lack of African designers in the industry. Ms. Ade stepped in as a solution to this problem with the debut of her first collection in 2013.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qxjWa8A.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Her brand is called BFyne</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gwO0C3D.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UzNtWGS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://bfyne.com/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/pCPnRRx</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GarfunkyLennon]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>nothing to wear, they say</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/w840D2U</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WOBW4XA.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/w840D2U</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[kurgypster]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Stand Name: Chancla</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/1vgOdk1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UYWtmhZ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#la_chancla #serious #run #hide_the_pain_harold #powerful #jojos_bizzare_adventure</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/1vgOdk1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[cleverpublic]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Images of Note: Green Among us</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/si47CoS</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Pzerksj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gWRehV0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0gHjfLK.gif" style="max-wi